Current way:
  # setup cmake-3.0 or cmake-3.8 in your path
  % cmake --version
  % ./cmake.sh

---------------------------------------------

Original way: edit path for your env in cmake.sh and sx.cmake

  % mkdir build
  % cd build
  % ../cmake.sh
  % make

Next way: edit and source bashrc-local so cmake 3.0 binary is found automatically

  $ mkdir build
  $ cd build
  $ cmake -DCMAKE_TOOLCHAIN_FILE=../sx.cmake ..
  $ make
